t: "They will make excuses to you ňĻbelieversňļ when you return to them. Say, ‚ÄúMake no excuses, ňĻforňļ we will not believe you. Allah has already informed us about your ňĻtrueňļ state ňĻof faithňļ. Your ňĻfutureňļ deeds will be observed by Allah and His Messenger as well. And you will be returned to the Knower of the seen and unseen, then He will inform you of what you used to do.‚ÄĚ"